This will be our fourth meeting to discuss things related to web development.

Like our previous meetings:
To help us get to know each other and facilitate discussion, with each participants permission, I will circulate a list of each participants; with a brief bio / areas of knowledge,...

So if you are joining us and haven't emailed your info for the participant list- do so ASAP- Thanks! and see you soon...
